text: The Nevadan is a 1950 American western movie. It was directed by Gordon Douglas. Actors include Randolph Scott, Dorothy Malone, Forrest Tucker, Frank Faylen, and George Macready. It was distributed by Columbia Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1950 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Gordon Douglas
